Summary: I'm submitting this for a friend. From his account of events he was just enjoying the mountainside and decided to photograph it. When he develpoed the film he found the object. He gave it to me so that I could possibly figure what it is.
divs: Sighting DetailsMy friend was on a recent trip to Hawaii, he was enjoying the mountainside and decided to take a photograph of what he was seeing. When he developed the photo he found that there was something in the photo that he did not see meanwhile taking the photograph. He thought to give it to me so that I can take a look and try to decipher what it could be. Since I am doing research about UFO's. I still have not been able to make heads or tails of it.
